{
  "texts": [
    "The feature aggregation module mainly includes the attention fusion and node feature aggregation modules.",
    "Attention Fusion is used to emphasize important information through the utilization of attention mechanisms for feature fusion.",
    "Node feature aggregation, on the other hand, aims to aggregate features from different channels to obtain the final representation of node features.",
    "The introduction of multi-channel graph convolution allows DeepMCGCN to simultaneously utilize information captured by different channels, providing a more comprehensive understanding of graph structures.",
    "This contributes to improved modeling of complex relationships and node features, thereby enhancing the model's performance."
  ]
}